51:55.277 --> 51:57.246
That's the lesson.

51:59.514 --> 52:02.252
I didn't know a single criminal
before that.

52:05.587 --> 52:07.623
Afterwards, I did.

52:21.304 --> 52:25.275
(BUZZING)

52:33.549 --> 52:35.382
Alright.

52:35.384 --> 52:38.288
Looks good.

52:40.389 --> 52:42.492
<i>Your momma woulda
liked that.</i>

53:01.543 --> 53:03.444
Nice car, Dean.

53:03.446 --> 53:05.746
(CLEARS THROAT)

53:05.748 --> 53:07.480
Is this a social visit, Jack?

53:07.482 --> 53:08.849
I don't know yet.

53:08.851 --> 53:10.683
I've been hearing
some rumblings.

53:10.685 --> 53:11.684
Rumblings?

53:11.686 --> 53:14.755
Yeah. You know Saxon's always
been trouble.

53:14.757 --> 53:15.889
Thanks for the update.

53:15.891 --> 53:17.458
The people he's in bed with,

53:17.460 --> 53:19.492
the kind of money
he's throwing around?

53:19.494 --> 53:20.828
It's a whole new league
of trouble.

53:20.830 --> 53:21.762
What're you talking about,
Jack?

53:21.764 --> 53:22.663
What bed?

53:22.665 --> 53:23.667
Who's money?

53:24.667 --> 53:25.668
Hank.

53:27.670 --> 53:29.570
He's been friends with Hank
since he was a pup.

53:29.572 --> 53:31.374
Hank senior.

53:35.744 --> 53:37.378
Look, I'm not my brother's
keeper, Jack.

53:37.380 --> 53:38.512
What's it got to do with me?

53:38.514 --> 53:40.514
He broke into the station
after your mother's file,

53:40.516 --> 53:41.751
for one.

53:46.989 --> 53:48.521
Why the hell would
he do that?

53:48.523 --> 53:50.757
He's your brother.

53:50.759 --> 53:51.958
You get him reigned in.

53:51.960 --> 53:52.759
Is that a warning?

53:52.761 --> 53:55.731
Get him reigned in or what?
Hmm?

53:56.831 --> 53:57.965
When did you get
so sensitive?

53:57.967 --> 54:00.933
Look, it's no secret we don't
like each other, Jack.

54:00.935 --> 54:03.670
I hate you like a poison,
actually.

54:03.672 --> 54:04.904
That's a heartbreaker.

54:04.906 --> 54:07.674
He thinks you had something
to do with his mother's death.

54:07.676 --> 54:09.942
Is that a heartbreaker,
Dean?

54:09.944 --> 54:12.445
What exactly do you want,
Jack?

54:12.447 --> 54:13.614
I thought you were the law
around here.

54:13.616 --> 54:14.480
Do your job.

54:14.482 --> 54:15.114
What do you want?

54:15.116 --> 54:16.416
My blessing to arrest him?

54:16.418 --> 54:17.451
Arrest him for what?

54:17.453 --> 54:18.451
Asking questions?

54:18.453 --> 54:19.953
Breaking into the police station
isn't enough?

54:19.955 --> 54:22.726
It was your fiancÃ©
who bailed him out.

54:26.694 --> 54:28.829
Oh, you didn't know?

54:28.831 --> 54:30.963
Amelia. She bailed him out.

54:30.965 --> 54:32.565
I thought you sent her.

54:32.567 --> 54:34.867
I was just trying
to protect you.

54:34.869 --> 54:36.772
Do me a favour, Jack.

54:39.842 --> 54:41.711
Don't protect me.

54:42.645 --> 54:49.849
(MUSIC BEGINS)

54:49.851 --> 54:58.592
<i>âª It's over, it's over,
it's over now, âª</i>

54:58.594 --> 55:07.467
<i>âª It's over, that's all there
